{"tid":275718,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"戴上headphone，先知我地需要既係安靜。","createTime":"2017-06-08T09:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T11:22:00.000Z","uid":93812,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67a091b9b56be657c04b844645bc43057dd247d4","tid":275718,"uid":93812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:05:57.000Z","msg":"放飯時間走左去大家樂叫左碗燒鴨米，<br />\n<br />\n坐低戴headphone開始嘆tea，<br />\n<br />\n食到一半先發現原來自己一直冇播歌，<br />\n<br />\n即係代表我處於寧靜狀態有一段時間，<br />\n<br />\n但係呢一刻我好舒服好自在，<br />\n<br />\n好似揾番自己本體咁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老實講，<br />\n<br />\n我地都好需要有安靜既空間。<br />\n<br />\n每日煩躁不安既社會模式令人作嘔，<br />\n<br />\n快、趕、完美已經成為社會既標準，<br />\n<br />\n為左追求達到標準唔容許有出錯，<br />\n<br />\n人只會逼使自己或他人meet target，<br />\n<br />\n煩躁不安正係失望帶黎既附屬品，<br />\n<br />\n安靜始乎離我地好遠。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n容許自己或他人做得唔好，<br />\n<br />\n應該係得到安靜既先決條件。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，試試放慢腳步打開心胸吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打完呢篇野之後，<br />\n<br />\n又要繼續開工了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d5d01ddf00ef1342b53b9d6d02671b5383d2cf","tid":275718,"uid":24469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人本來就是寂寞的"},{"pid":"6ba770639280420279397621385f05c66921b1e0","tid":275718,"uid":93812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f387ad5597add9ded1a5fd1b0b5deb42ced3aab6","tid":275718,"uid":93812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T11:22:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}